plot: Colt pleads with Zeke to not use his scream and turn Falco into a Titan. All the while, soldiers and Titans clash in battle as Eren struggles to make contact with his brother.

With Zeke incapacitated and Eren heavily injured, Eren must try to reach Zeke to finally unleash the power of the Founding Titan. Reiner and Galliard try desperately to stop him, while Pieck continues to rain fire from above and fight off the Yeagerists. Gabi, Falco, and Colt try to also try reach Zeke before he summons enough strength to scream, releasing the titans and dooming Falco and the rest of the officers who drank the wine. Many characters have to make difficult decisions and learn more of the truth about their past and their world.—sspencer-813-220025
